style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "微软雅黑",sans-serif; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt'>企业发生重组业务，按照《通知》第五条第（一）项要求，企业在备案或提交确认申请时，应从以下方面说明企业重组具有合理的商业目的：<SPAN 
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="BACKGROUND: white; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 11.25pt 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><A name=No85_Z3T18K1X1></A><SPAN 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "微软雅黑",sans-serif; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt'>（一）重组活动的交易方式。即重组活动采取的具体形式、交易背景、交易时间、在交易之前和之后的运作方式和有关的商业常规；<SPAN 
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="BACKGROUND: white; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 11.25pt 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><A name=No86_Z3T18K1X2></A><SPAN 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "微软雅黑",sans-serif; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt'>（二）该项交易的形式及实质。即形式上交易所产生的法律权利和责任，也是该项交易的法律后果。另外，交易实际上或商业上产生的最终结果；<SPAN 
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="BACKGROUND: white; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 11.25pt 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><A name=No87_Z3T18K1X3></A><SPAN 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "微软雅黑",sans-serif; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt'>（三）重组活动给交易各方税务状况带来的可能变化；<SPAN 
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="BACKGROUND: white; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 11.25pt 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><A name=No88_Z3T18K1X4></A><SPAN 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "微软雅黑",sans-serif; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt'>（四）重组各方从交易中获得的财务状况变化；<SPAN 
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="BACKGROUND: white; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 11.25pt 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
